        <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
            Are you <span class="text-red-600">Bolloré'd ?</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
            Vérifiez instantanément si un média, une marque ou une entreprise appartient à la galaxie de la famille Bolloré.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mt-8">
            <input 
                type="text" 
                id="barreRecherche" 
                placeholder="Ex: CNews, Havas, Gameloft..." 
                class="w-full sm:w-96 px-5 py-4 text-lg border-2 border-slate-200 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:border-red-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-red-500 shadow-sm transition-all"
                onkeypress="gererToucheEntree(event)"
            >
            <button 
                onclick="lancerRecherche()" 
                class="px-8 py-4 bg-slate-900 hover:bg-slate-800 text-white font-bold rounded-xl text-lg shadow-md transition-colors"
            >
                Vérifier
            </button>
        </div>

        <div id="zoneResultat" class="mt-10 hidden text-left p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border-l-8">
